==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Provoking
<hw>Pro*vok"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having the power or quality of
exciting resentment; tending to awaken passion or vexation; <as>as,
<ex>provoking</ex> words or treatment</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Pro*vok"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Provost</ent>⟦br⟧
